popup.message:
This model requires another model in your pack to function correctly.

Create chest_right.jem using a text editor and put the following contents inside it:

{"models":[{"part":"base"},{"part":"lid"},{"part":"knob"}]}

entities.name: iron_golem_destroy_stages
entities.description: A custom version of the Iron Golem which allows you to model each stage of it cracking independently from one another

entities.name: mooshroom_mushrooms
entities.description: A custom version of the Mooshroom with the mushrooms modelled on top

popup.title: Before you start...
popup.message:
This model requires some extra textures in your resource pack to function correctly:

assets/minecraft/textures/entity/cow/red_mushroom.png
assets/minecraft/textures/entity/cow/brown_mushroom.png

These textures need to be created manually, and should be 1x1 transparent images.
